  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study to verify the superiority of ramosetron hydrochloride (Irribow Tablets) to placebo
      for male patients with diarrhea-predominant irritable bowel syndrome (D-IBS) and to evaluate
      its safety.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
